  "steps": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "instruction": "Heat chicken stock until boiling using whatever method you choose (stove, 3 - 4 minutes in microwave on high)."
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Pour over couscous in a heatproof bowl. Shake to level the couscous, cover with plate (or cling wrap)."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Leave for 10 minutes, then fluff with fork. Stir through olive oil, lemon juice and salt."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Stir through either herbs or fruit &amp; nuts. Or as I do, use it all! Keep warm until ready to use. Ideal served with Tagine, or anything Middle Eastern."
